          "name": "Travel Guide",
          "page": 99,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "A cultural symbol for Irrisen, the Irriseni owlbear is particularly well adapted to frosty conditions. These owlbears are larger than their temperate zone counterparts.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
